# MCP Server Configuration Template
# 
# This is an example configuration file for MCP servers.
# To use this file:
# 1. Copy it to create your actual config: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace all placeholder values with your actual API keys
# 3. See API_KEYS_GUIDE.md for detailed instructions on obtaining these keys
#
# SECURITY: Never commit your actual .env file to git!

# ==============================================================================
# SLACK CONFIGURATION
# ==============================================================================
# Your Slack bot token - starts with 'xoxb-'
# Get this from: https://api.slack.com/apps (see API_KEYS_GUIDE.md)
SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-your-slack-bot-token-here

# Your Slack team/workspace ID - starts with 'T' followed by 8-10 characters
# Find this in: Slack settings > Workspace settings > Workspace ID
SLACK_TEAM_ID=T1234ABCD

# ==============================================================================
# LINEAR CONFIGURATION
# ==============================================================================
# Your Linear API key - starts with 'lin_api_'
# Get this from: Linear > Settings > API > Create key
# Or ask your Linear admin for a shared key
LINEAR_API_KEY=lin_api_your-linear-api-key-here

# ==============================================================================
# NOTION CONFIGURATION
# ==============================================================================
# Your Notion integration token - starts with 'secret_'
# Get this from: https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
# Remember to share pages with your integration!
NOTION_TOKEN=secret_your-notion-integration-token-here

# ==============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: ZAPIER CONFIGURATION (for Otter.ai integration)
# ==============================================================================
# Uncomment these lines if you want to use Otter.ai transcripts via Zapier
# ZAPIER_API_KEY=your-zapier-api-key-here
# OTTER_ZAPIER_ENDPOINT=https://hooks.zapier.com/hooks/catch/YOUR-WEBHOOK-ID

# ==============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING TIPS
# ==============================================================================
# 
# If you're getting "Invalid token" errors:
# - Make sure you copied the ENTIRE token (they're long!)
# - Check that Slack token starts with 'xoxb-' not 'xoxp-'
# - Verify Linear key starts with 'lin_api_'
# - Ensure Notion token starts with 'secret_'
#
# For more help, see:
# - API_KEYS_GUIDE.md - Detailed setup instructions
# - SETUP_GUIDE.md - Complete setup walkthrough
# - troubleshoot-mcp.sh - Automated troubleshooting script